Package: simulateR
Type: Package
Title: Test Statistical Models Through Simulation
Version: 0.1.2
Date: 2016-08-03
Author@R: person("Jeffrey", "Hughes", email="jeff.hughes@gmail.com",
    role=c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package allows you to run simulations while easily varying
    parameters. One common use case would be to estimate statistical power for
    complex models. See the simulateR documentation for more information,
    documentation, and examples.
License: GPL-3
LazyData: TRUE
